_types": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": null, "hotel_class": "standard", "is_featured": false, "price_range": null, "star_rating": 3, "best_seasons": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Morioka Aishinkan", "workspace_id": "aed1bc23-7bbf-4c59-a8e3-12dbb3271f0a", "booking_email": null, "booking_phone": "019-623-1456", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "butler_service": false, "certifications": null, "deleted_reason": null, "description_en": null, "dining_options": null, "group_friendly": true, "internal_notes": "盛岡愛真館飯店注意事項\n\n分本館跟別館兩棟，房間為和式跟洋式兩種。這次全員住別館。\n\n房間互撥  2+房號\n早餐自助餐 6：30 ~\n2樓『朝日之間』，憑鑰匙自由入場，座位自由席。晚餐跟早餐相同地方\n\n飯店wifi ID：aishinwifi\n密碼：aishinwifi\n早call是7：00\n出發是8：30\n\n建議各位貴賓自己手機也要設個鬧鐘，以防飯店電話聲音太小叫不醒您喲！\n飯店館內全面禁煙，有抽菸的貴賓，需請移駕到1樓吸煙區抽煙，房內不能抽喲！會被罰錢喲！如需吹風機請跟櫃檯借或是到大浴場使用。\n\n室內大浴場  別館3樓\n ~01：00為止\n隔天早上5：00開始\n\n庭園繩文露天溫泉  本館3樓\n~22：00為止（最後入場21：00）\n隔天早上5：00開始\n毛巾在房內，請攜帶至大浴場使用，使用完畢請帶回房間\n浴衣和拖鞋，館內、餐廳皆可使用喲！\n隔天早上溫泉的男女湯場地會互換，請小心不要跑錯地方喲！\n一樓賣點店營業時間：7：00-21：00\n一樓大廳有酒類飲料免費供應至22:00, 其他軟性飲料跟咖啡則24小時免費供應。\n\n浴衣房間有放M尺寸，若需其他尺寸的話，在各樓層電梯旁，請依照身高拿取適合您的尺寸，腰帶在衣櫃裡", "max_group_size": null, "booking_contact": null, "commission_rate": null, "google_maps_url": null, "airport_transfer": false, "concierge_service": true, "restaurants_count": null, "avg_price_per_night": null, "min_rooms_for_group": null, "group_rate_available": false, "has_michelin_restaurant": false}, {"id": "2d0347b3-b269-4e83-ba29-b7e905c7394a", "fax": null, "name": "大阪 welina 心齋橋 和NAGOMI", "brand": null, "notes": null, "phone": null, "awards": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "osaka", "website": null, "category": "飯店 / Hotel", "currency": "USD", "latitude": null, "amenities": null, "is_active": true, "longitude": null, "region_id": null, "address_en": null, "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2026-03-16T07:42:37.320998+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "facilities": null, "highlights": null, "name_local": "大阪 welina 心斎橋 和NAGOMI", "room_types": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": null, "hotel_class": "standard", "is_featured": false, "price_range": null, "star_rating": 3, "best_seasons": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Osaka Welina Shinsaibashi and NAGOMI", "workspace_id": "aed1bc23-7bbf-4c59-a8e3-12dbb3271f0a", "booking_email": null, "booking_phone": null, "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "butler_service": false, "certifications": null, "deleted_reason": null, "description_en": null, "dining_options": null, "group_friendly": true, "internal_notes": "進去飯店內都要脫鞋子。\n會給房卡跟鞋櫃號碼（進去飯店要脫鞋，換室內拖鞋），鞋櫃建議上鎖（上鎖方式另外說明），因為好幾次有人穿錯鞋或被別人亂放。\n\n☎️房號互撥：1+房號\n🌟叫早時間：請自行設定（飯店不提供）\n\n🍞早餐餐廳：1樓<自助餐> 7:00-9:00\n🌟自行用餐🌟需餐卷，座位只有28個，請早點去用餐。\n\n👔有投幣式洗衣機\n\n🛗電梯只有一台，請感應房卡才能按樓層，而且只能去到自己的樓層，無法到別的樓層去，安全性高。退房需歸還，請妥善保管，遺失將酌收手續費。\n\n🚭全館禁煙。吸菸室：1樓戶外右手邊\n\n📳 wifi\nID: Welina_Hotel\nPASSWORD：welinahotel\n\n👟🔑鞋櫃鎖方式\n1. 鑰匙孔為「ㄧ」，右邊4碼的數字原先設0000，請自行調成數字密碼。例如0987。\n2. 將鑰匙孔90度轉成「l」，就是鎖上。把0987調成其他數字就打不開。\n3. 請記得最後退房要調回「0000」，以方便下一個人使用。", "max_group_size": null, "booking_contact": null, "commission_rate": null, "google_maps_url": null, "airport_transfer": false, "concierge_service": true, "restaurants_count": null, "avg_price_per_night": null, "min_rooms_for_group": null, "group_rate_available": false, "has_michelin_restaurant": false}, {"id": "2d11c7f6-bc78-490c-9dfd-9cbb87a54158", "fax": null, "name": "界 京都", "brand": "星野集團 - 界", "notes": null, "phone": null, "awards": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "kyoto", "website": null, "category": "溫泉旅館", "currency": "USD", "latitude": null, "amenities": null, "is_active": true, "longitude": null, "region_id": null, "address_en": null, "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2026-04-04T11:26:52.21+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "facilities": null, "highlights": null, "name_local": null, "room_types": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T2