, "group_friendly": true, "internal_notes": null, "max_group_size": null, "booking_contact": null, "commission_rate": null, "google_maps_url": null, "airport_transfer": false, "concierge_service": true, "restaurants_count": null, "avg_price_per_night": null, "min_rooms_for_group": null, "group_rate_available": false, "has_michelin_restaurant": false}, {"id": "3e4b6f61-864e-4c9e-bb3b-5ddbf7f1bf28", "fax": null, "name": "APA海濱幕張酒店", "brand": null, "notes": null, "phone": "043-296-0111", "awards": null, "images": null, "address": "千葉県千葉市美浜区ひび野2-3", "city_id": "tokyo", "website": null, "category": "飯店 / Hotel", "currency": "USD", "latitude": null, "amenities": null, "is_active": true, "longitude": null, "region_id": null, "address_en": null, "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2026-03-16T07:42:37.320998+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "facilities": null, "highlights": null, "name_local": "APAホテル&リゾート東京ベイ幕張", "room_types": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": null, "hotel_class": "standard", "is_featured": false, "price_range": null, "star_rating": 3, "best_seasons": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "APA Hotel & Resort Tokyo Bay Makuhari", "workspace_id": "aed1bc23-7bbf-4c59-a8e3-12dbb3271f0a", "booking_email": null, "booking_phone": "043-296-0111", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "butler_service": false, "certifications": null, "deleted_reason": null, "description_en": null, "dining_options": null, "group_friendly": true, "internal_notes": "⭕️連住兩天不換房，現在改成不清掃就不用做任何動作。要清掃就貼牌子。如果想清掃才要貼牌子若要清掃房間，也請將貴重物品鎖至行李箱中。\n\n👽領隊房號：\n ☎️房間對撥：8+房號\n\n⏰叫早時間：\n🚌出發時間：\n     集合地點：本館1樓大廳\n\n🍞早餐餐廳：本館1樓 6:30開始\n⭐️自行用餐，需要早餐卷\n\n🌞降雨：%\n🌡️溫度：度\n\n📳WIFI密碼\nPASSWORD：電視打開後，在畫面上會顯示密碼。\n\n🛗分左右兩邊，右高25-45左低1-25樓層，請確認後再搭乘。\n\n🚬吸煙區：戶外，出門後左轉大巴士停車場旁。\n\n🔑房卡不可遺失，請妥善保管\n♨ 溫泉浴場：\n⭕️憑房卡入場\n大浴場：中央棟4樓\n入浴時間：14:00-02:00（01:30最後入場）\n\n⭐️大小毛巾自己從房間裡帶過去\n（小毛巾可以下湯，大毛巾請放在旁邊籃子或櫃子裡），泡湯盡可能結伴同行，泡15分鐘休息10分鐘。請注意安全。⭕️站起來前，請讓心臟超過水面30-60秒，再緩緩起身。\n\n🏪便利商店Lawson ：1樓與2樓（24H)\n\n💊藥妝店：松本清，3樓，營業至23:00。\n\n回程電車方式\n⭕️1. 確保搭乘「京葉線」或「武藏野線直通京葉線」\n\t•\t京葉線（快速 / 各停）：直達海濱幕張站，無需換車\n\t•\t武藏野線直通列車（有些來自八王子、府中本町等地）也可能行駛至海濱幕張\n\n❌2. 避免誤搭「京葉線的西船橋方向支線」\n\t•\t部分京葉線列車會開往「西船橋站」（例如「各站停車（各停）」的西船橋行），這些列車不會到達海濱幕張\n\t•\t解決辦法：若不小心搭上了「西船橋行」，可以在南船橋站下車，轉乘前往**蘇我方向（海濱幕張）**的列車\n\n3. 京葉線「快速」與「各停」的差別\n\t•\t快速（快速）：停靠站較少，從舞濱到海濱幕張大約 16 分鐘\n\t•\t各站停車（各停）：每站都停，大約 20 分鐘", "max_group_size": null, "booking_contact": null, "commission_rate": null, "google_maps_url": null, "airport_transfer": false, "concierge_service": true, "restaurants_count": null, "avg_price_per_night": null, "min_rooms_for_group": null, "group_rate_available": false, "has_michelin_restaurant": false}, {"id": "3ead3cc4-bd98-406f-b312-43d04b76797b", "fax": null, "name": "OMO5 Okinawa Naha by Hoshino Resorts", "brand": null, "notes": null, "phone": null, "awards": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "himeji", "website": null, "category": "飯店 / Hotel", "currency": "USD", "latitude": null, "amenities": null, "is_active": true, "longitude": null, "region_id": null, "address_en": null, "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2026-03-24T06:40:29.409271+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "facilities": null, "highlights": null, "name_local": null, "room_types": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": null, "hotel_class": null, "is_featured": false, "price_range": null, "star_rating": null, "best_seasons": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": null, "workspace_id": "aed1bc23-7bbf-4c59-a8e3-12dbb3271f0a", "booking_email": null, "booking_phone": null, "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "butler_service": false, "certifications": null, "deleted_reason": null, "description_en": null, "dining_options": null, "group_friendly": true, "internal_notes": null, "max_group_size": null, "booking_contact": null, "commission_rate": null, "google_maps_url": null, "airport_t