浜", "room_types": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": null, "hotel_class": "standard", "is_featured": false, "price_range": null, "star_rating": 3, "best_seasons": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Hyatt Regency Yokohama", "workspace_id": "aed1bc23-7bbf-4c59-a8e3-12dbb3271f0a", "booking_email": null, "booking_phone": "045-222-1234", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "butler_service": false, "certifications": null, "deleted_reason": null, "description_en": null, "dining_options": null, "group_friendly": true, "internal_notes": "橫濱凱悅酒店： \n \n早餐Harbor Kitchen \n時間：07:00開始 \n樓層：2樓 \n報房號即可 \n \nWiFi 密碼：hyattyokohama2020 \n \n房間互打70+房號 \n \n房內有提供免費水，不夠可再打電話請櫃檯提供。 \n \n*飯店大廳出來右邊有超商 \n \n健身房24小時\n\n玄～箱根強羅 \n🔺明天(5/10)早上9：30大廳集合出發，鑰匙記得還給櫃檯。\n🔺明天早上9：00前，請把行李拿到房門外，服務員會去收。\n🔺明天伊豆最高溫約19度，請攜帶所需物品及保暖衣物。\n\n🔹晚餐18：00，1樓宴會廳，日式會席料理。馬醬18：00在1樓等大家。\n🔹早餐特別安排於房內享用，8：00飯店人員會將餐點送至各位貴賓的房間內，和式定食。\n🔹房內皆有泉掛式溫泉。房門不會自動上鎖，出門記得鎖門。房內有浴衣、拖鞋都可以穿去泡湯、用餐⋯\n🔹大浴場在B1樓，5：00～//凌晨01:00止，大小毛巾溫泉區都有。\n🔹房間冰箱內有酒精及無酒精飲料皆為免費。(水、啤酒、烏龍茶、果凍等⋯）\n🔹 有wifi，無需密碼。\n🔹1樓大廳有休息區，備有酒水、飲料、點心可免費享用時間15：00～18：00，20：00～23:00止，提供免費飲品、啤酒、紅白酒、點心。(20：00之後提供燒酌及威士忌）\n🔹賣店，07:30-21:00，1樓大廳。\n🔹內線撥打，1+房號電話。", "max_group_size": null, "booking_contact": null, "commission_rate": null, "google_maps_url": null, "airport_transfer": false, "concierge_service": true, "restaurants_count": null, "avg_price_per_night": null, "min_rooms_for_group": null, "group_rate_available": false, "has_michelin_restaurant": false}, {"id": "48396c78-08f7-496b-9c33-f61cbef8cfe6", "fax": null, "name": "HOTEL USJ PORT", "brand": null, "notes": null, "phone": "06-6463-5000", "awards": null, "images": null, "address": "大阪府大阪市此花区咲洲5丁目6番16号", "city_id": "osaka", "website": null, "category": "飯店 / Hotel", "currency": "USD", "latitude": null, "amenities": null, "is_active": true, "longitude": null, "region_id": null, "address_en": null, "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2026-03-16T07:42:49.916557+00:00