 false, "display_order": 0, "butler_service": false, "certifications": null, "deleted_reason": null, "description_en": null, "dining_options": null, "group_friendly": true, "internal_notes": null, "max_group_size": null, "booking_contact": null, "commission_rate": null, "google_maps_url": null, "airport_transfer": false, "concierge_service": true, "restaurants_count": null, "avg_price_per_night": null, "min_rooms_for_group": null, "group_rate_available": false, "has_michelin_restaurant": false}, {"id": "62fc5bba-58ed-469e-9bff-49d20376930c", "fax": null, "name": "萬座王子飯店", "brand": null, "notes": null, "phone": "0279-98-1111", "awards": null, "images": null, "address": "群馬県吾妻郡嬬恋村万座温泉", "city_id": "tokyo", "website": null, "category": "飯店 / Hotel", "currency": "USD", "latitude": null, "amenities": null, "is_active": true, "longitude": null, "region_id": null, "address_en": null, "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2026-03-16T07:42:53.700329+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "facilities": null, "highlights": null, "name_local": "万座プリンスホテル", "room_types": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": null, "hotel_class": "standard", "is_featured": false, "price_range": null, "star_rating": 3, "best_seasons": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Manza Prince Hotel", "workspace_id": "aed1bc23-7bbf-4c59-a8e3-12dbb3271f0a", "booking_email": null, "booking_phone": "0279-98-1111", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "butler_service": false, "certifications": null, "deleted_reason": null, "description_en": null, "dining_options": null, "group_friendly": true, "internal_notes": "⭕️位於海拔1800公尺，全館無冷氣空調，僅有暖氣設備，可開點窗+放杯水比較舒服。\n⭕️。晚餐2樓，時間到飯店再報告。\n\n👽領隊房號：\n☎️房號互撥：8+房間號碼\n\n⏰明天叫早時間：❌ 櫃檯無法設定，請自訂手機鬧鐘06:00，或拿起客房的電話按770600\n🚌出發時間：\n\n🍱晚餐：集合用餐，餐廳在本館2樓，時間再報告。\n\n🍞早餐餐廳：\n本館2樓（自助餐）06:30-10:00\n⭐️自行用餐⭐️帶房卡\n\n🌞明天降雨：%\n🌡️溫度：度\n\n🏨飯店大廳：本館1樓\n🔑鑰匙為感應式卡片（1人1卡，不佔床無），請妥善保管，遺失會索賠¥1500\n\n📳WIFI密碼\nID:PRINCE-HOTEL\nPASSWORD：welcomeph\n\n🚭全館禁煙🚬 ：吸煙區：面對本館1樓電梯右手邊上樓梯的小房間。\n😔房間內吸煙會罰款產生¥20000\n⭐️請勿心存僥倖，即使在外面抽，煙灰、煙蒂也請別帶回房間垃圾桶。開放至今，已發生多起，別團團員賠錢事件。\n\n♨️溫泉：本館1樓入口往下（東館2樓出電梯直走），營業時間24小時。🌟請帶著您房間内的毛巾前往。（白色大浴巾為擦拭拿體用，請在更衣間使用，白色毛巾請不要浸到溫泉内，以免沾染顏色和味道)\n\n⭐️若欲使用男女混浴的溫泉，請使用房間内混浴專用綠色毛巾，若數量不足可向櫃合索取。\n或是至販賣店購買混浴專用穿著(男性用¥550、女性用¥1,100)(禁止穿著泳衣入浴)\n❗️‼️ 《使用露天溫泉時》\n由於地面濕滑，請留意您的腳步，小心慢行\n❗️泡湯盡可能結伴同行，泡15分鐘休息10分鐘。吃完飯後40分鐘後再泡。\n‼️如有飲酒請2小時後再泡，請注意安全。\n⭕️起身時一定要讓心臟超過水面30秒以上再緩緩起身，避免暈厥。\n\n🚫謝絕刺青者\n🙏入浴的禮節：\n致親愛的旅客\n使用溫泉時請遵守以下注意事項\n1.請將身體洗淨，再進入大浴池\n2.請輕聱細語勿大聲喧嘩及嬉鬧\n3. 請勿把毛巾及頭髮浸泡在溫泉裡\n4.衣服及拖鞋無法穿著進入浴場\n\n🛒賣店：在本館1樓，08:30-20:00\n\n🛍️請將明日白天有可能使用的保溫瓶，隨身小物，防曬禦暑用品，裝在隨身行李，放置巴士位置上\n\n😱溫馨提醒\n⭐️離開房間，請回頭看一眼書桌、衣櫥、冰箱、浴室。\n掉東西第一名：充電器。第二名：化妝包。第三名：耳環首飾類。\n\n⭐️明早大廳1樓，會有行李置物處（）的看板，建議您可以在吃早餐前，就先整理好行李置放，比較不會掉東西。", "max_group_size": null, "booking_contact": null, "commission_rate": null, "google_maps_url": null, "airport_transfer": false, "concierge_service": true, "restaurants_count": null, "avg_price_per_night": null, "min_rooms_for_group": null, "group_rate_available": false, "has_michelin_restaurant": false}, {"id": "6467196f-78ab-4da9-b64d-6dac33e1ba57", "fax": null, "name": "界 別府", "brand": "星野集團 - 界", "notes": null, "phone": null, "awards": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "tokyo", "website": null, "category": "精品溫泉旅館", "currency": "USD", "latitude": null, "amenities": null, "is_active": true, "longitude": null, "region_id": null, "address_en": null, "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2026-04-04T11:39:11.948+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "facilities": null, "highlights": null, "name_local": null, "room_types": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": null, "hotel_class": "高端精品", "is_featured": true, "price_range": null, "star_rating": 4, "best_seasons": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Kai Beppu", "workspace_id": "aed1bc23-7bbf-4c59-a8e3-12dbb3271f0a", "booking_email": null, "booking_phone": null, "data_ver