ya Onsen Hotel", "workspace_id": "aed1bc23-7bbf-4c59-a8e3-12dbb3271f0a", "booking_email": null, "booking_phone": "0576-25-2323", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "butler_service": false, "certifications": null, "deleted_reason": null, "description_en": null, "dining_options": null, "group_friendly": true, "internal_notes": "三好屋溫泉飯店注意事項\n\n房間互撥  1+房號\n（阿琇 直播3206 ）\n\n早餐   自助餐 2樓   \n7：00~報房號入場即可\n                   \n大浴場 7樓\n15：00~01：00\n02：00~隔天11：00為止\n\n女湯、男湯，2點後場地會互換喲！\n\n露天溫泉\n~00：00為止，隔天6：00~\n在大浴場外有聯絡通道，爬上93階，即可泡湯\n現場只有更衣區，沒有洗浴空間，請在室內大浴場洗澡後，再過去泡喲！\n\n大小毛巾在房內，請攜帶至大浴場使用，使用完畢請帶回房間\n\n浴衣和拖鞋館內、餐廳皆可來回使用\n\n浴衣穿法右下左上，切勿相反喲！\n\n抽煙請到1樓 外面左側吸煙室，切勿在房內抽煙，會被罰錢喲！\n\n飯店WIFI ID：yukainet\n密碼：11088011\n\n明日8：00出發，1樓集合\n7：50開始陸續上行李喲！\n\n已請飯店明早在1樓櫃檯附近設置行李置放區（百威旅遊  8：00出發  阿琇），可寄放行李後，再去用早餐喲！\n\n早call是6點，建議各位貴賓自己手機也要設個鬧鐘，以防飯店電話聲音太小叫不醒您喲！\n\n房間的熱水是溫泉，若需飲用自來水，請轉到冷水取用喲！", "max_group_size": null, "booking_contact": null, "commission_rate": null, "google_maps_url": null, "airport_transfer": false, "concierge_service": true, "restaurants_count": null, "avg_price_per_night": null, "min_rooms_for_group": null, "group_rate_available": false, "has_michelin_restaurant": false}, {"id": "6677699f-814c-40dd-ae6e-587765b0cc4d", "fax": null, "name": "巴生益馬温德姆酒店", "brand": null, "notes": null, "phone": null, "awards": null, "images": ["https://wzvwmawpkapcmkfmkvav.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/resources/hotels/6677699f-814c-40dd-ae6e-587765b0cc4d/1775811839451_q6kwmoyxipr.webp"], "address": "", "city_id": "ipoh", "website": null, "category": "飯店 / Hotel", "currency": "USD", "latitude": null, "amenities": null, "is_active": true, "longitude": null, "region_id": null, "address_en": null, "country_id": "malaysia", "created_at": "2026-04-10T09:03:27.502891+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "facilities": null, "highlights": null, "name_local": null, "room_types": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "