 "amenities": null, "is_active": true, "longitude": null, "region_id": null, "address_en": null, "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2026-03-16T07:42:37.898421+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "facilities": null, "highlights": null, "name_local": "クインテッサホテル 福岡天神南", "room_types": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": null, "hotel_class": "standard", "is_featured": false, "price_range": null, "star_rating": 3, "best_seasons": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Quintessa Hotel Fukuoka Tenjin Minami", "workspace_id": "aed1bc23-7bbf-4c59-a8e3-12dbb3271f0a", "booking_email": null, "booking_phone": null, "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "butler_service": false, "certifications": null, "deleted_reason": null, "description_en": null, "dining_options": null, "group_friendly": true, "internal_notes": "1樓有吸菸室、製冰機、販賣機、洗衣房、微波爐\n\n06：30 1樓可以吃早餐（需餐券）", "max_group_size": null, "booking_contact": null, "commission_rate": null, "google_maps_url": null, "airport_transfer": false, "concierge_service": true, "restaurants_count": null, "avg_price_per_night": null, "min_rooms_for_group": null, "group_rate_available": false, "has_michelin_restaurant": false}, {"id": "9679bc5b-9ca2-47e2-854d-4d6c6a0c92d8", "fax": null, "name": "星野渡假村 Risonare Tomamu", "brand": null, "notes": null, "phone": "0167-58-1111", "awards": null, "images": null, "address": "北海道勇払郡占冠村字中トマム", "city_id": "tokyo", "website": null, "category": "飯店 / Hotel", "currency": "USD", "latitude": null, "amenities": null, "is_active": true, "longitude": null, "region_id": null, "address_en": null, "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2026-03-16T07:42:47.361991+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "facilities": null, "highlights": null, "name_local": "星野リゾート　リゾナーレトマム", "room_types": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": null, "hotel_class": "standard", "is_featured": false, "price_range": null, "star_rating": 3, "best_seasons": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Hoshino Resorts RISONARE Tomamu", "workspace_id": "aed1bc23-7bbf-4c59-a8e3-12dbb3271f0a", "booking_email": null, "booking_phone": "0167-58-1111", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "butler_service": false, "certifications": null, "deleted_reason": null, "description_en": null, "dining_options": null, "group_friendly": true, "internal_notes": "TOMAMU ，リゾナーレトマム\n 注意事項：\n到達時我們會在車內作說明，給大家一房一信封，裏面有纜車票，餐廳介紹，飯店園區地圖，房鎖，說明完發完信封再下車，\nwifi 不用密碼\n看雲海04：20起床04：50集合大約06：30回房間\n6：30起床07：00吃早餐，8：50上行李退房還房鎖，9：00準時出發\n \n🔺鑰匙信封套內會有\n1️⃣鑰匙\n\n🚌回住宿房間，接駁車坐到「J」\n（今晚入住處）\n\n2️⃣早餐券（可自由選擇餐廳，兩個自助餐）06:30始。\n@「Nininupri」\n🚌接駁車坐到「I」\n@「hal 」\n🚌接駁車坐到「E」\n\n建議選擇「Nininupri」\n🚌接駁車坐到「I」\n\n3️⃣一張泳池“微笑海灘”、浴場的無限次數使用券\n📍泳池（11:00～20:00，最後入場19:00）\n📍木林之湯（15:00～23:00，最後入場22:00）\n毛巾現場提供，「需」穿一般服裝、鞋子過去\n🚌接駁車坐到「C」\n\n⭐️備註：\n抵達微笑海灘後，在一樓聽完注意事項，之後下手扶梯更衣。\n\n⭐️備註：\n在溫泉拖鞋處對面是置物櫃，使用說明：\n1.打開置物櫃內有插槽、\n2.將藍色溫泉游泳券插入、\n3.自行輸入四位數字密碼即可上鎖\n\n5️⃣雲海平台纜車一次來回券\n🚌接駁車坐到「B」\n是否可搭乘纜車需看當天天氣狀況。\n纜車運行時間\n05:00-08:00\n首班纜車可由房間電視11頻道確認所有渡假村設施資訊，包括纜車是否運行。\n可坐7號巡迴車、兩站後下車\n纜車單趟搭乘約15分鐘。\n\n\n6️⃣一張飯店餐廳的介紹，想看菜單請掃簡介最後面的QRcode 就可以看菜單及價格；晚餐有14家餐廳可以選擇。\n\n⭐️住宿棟介紹：\n飯店進入大廳之後右手邊是吸煙室，左手邊是櫃檯；\n經過櫃檯後於路口左轉後經過側門及賣店，可前往E棟聯絡通道以及Tower 1電梯。\n賣店ザ・タワー07：00-22：00\n賣店リゾナーレトマム　8：00-22：00\n沿聯絡通道步行五分鐘～十分鐘或接駁車🚌可以坐到「E」後可抵達\n水之教堂 接駁車請坐到 E \n營業時間：20:30-21:30\n\n\n若經過大廳櫃檯後於路口右轉這刻通往I棟。\nG棟與I棟之間的聯絡通道步行約須15分鐘。\n途中沿途會順序經過早餐套餐餐廳Millay以及Forests mall和Hotalu Street。\n\n📍📍房間互撥\n1️⃣房號三碼：10 +房號\n2️⃣房號四碼： 1+房號\n\n📍明天出發：09:00，全員退房到齊後巴士才可開至玄關。\n📍明日天氣：\n📍行李暫放處會在玄關兩個玻璃門中間。", "max_group_size": null, "booking_contact": null, "commission_rate": null, "google_maps_url": null, "airport_transfer": false, "concierge_service": true, "restaurants_count": null, "avg_price_per_night": null, "min_rooms_for_group": null, "group_rate_available": false, "has_michelin_restaurant": false}, {"id": "96a95ee6-8e38-4e6b-ac13-a2ef1c46cd58", "fax": null, "name": "京都