nWiFi: H-CLEMENT\n密碼：86563111", "max_group_size": null, "booking_contact": null, "commission_rate": null, "google_maps_url": null, "airport_transfer": false, "concierge_service": true, "restaurants_count": null, "avg_price_per_night": null, "min_rooms_for_group": null, "group_rate_available": false, "has_michelin_restaurant": false}, {"id": "b657c389-8e3f-4081-b9e7-0be600528049", "fax": null, "name": "Izu Hotel Resort & Spa", "brand": null, "notes": null, "phone": "0557-37-3111", "awards": null, "images": null, "address": "静岡県伊東市伊豆高原4-1258-1", "city_id": "tokyo", "website": null, "category": "飯店 / Hotel", "currency": "USD", "latitude": null, "amenities": null, "is_active": true, "longitude": null, "region_id": null, "address_en": null, "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2026-03-16T07:42:44.111124+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "facilities": null, "highlights": null, "name_local": "伊豆ホテル リゾート＆スパ", "room_types": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": null, "hotel_class": "standard", "is_featured": false, "price_range": null, "star_rating": 3, "best_seasons": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Izu Hotel Resort & Spa", "workspace_id": "aed1bc23-7bbf-4c59-a8e3-12dbb3271f0a", "booking_email": null, "booking_phone": "0557-37-3111", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "butler_service": false, "certifications": null, "deleted_reason": null, "description_en": null, "dining_options": null, "group_friendly": true, "internal_notes": "伊豆溫泉 RESORT & SPA 飯店資訊\n\n🔺明天9/26早上10：00大廳出發，飯店櫃檯在玄關棟 5F，鑰匙記得還給櫃檯。\n🔺明天早上9：30前，請把行李拿到房門外，服務員會去收。\n🔺明天伊豆最高溫約21度，東京約23度，請攜帶所需物品及保暖衣物。\n\n🔹晚餐時間前半部17：30，後半部19 : 30西棟4樓，法式料理，小涵17：30在4樓等大家。\n🔹早餐8：00，和晚餐地點相同，洋式套餐。\n🔹房間在西棟，房內皆有溫泉。浴衣拖鞋只能穿到大浴場，其他地方請穿著一般服裝。\n🔹有WIFI帳號密碼都在信封內。 \n🔹冰箱飲料、酒水皆為免費。\n🔹 西棟1樓longe 7:00～21:00提供免費咖啡、紅茶等飲品及小點心，14:00～17：30提供紅白酒、啤酒等～\n🔹溫泉在西棟3樓，06:00~24：00，大小毛巾浴場都有準備。\n🔹4樓，展望足湯 10：00-22：00。 🔹3樓，深湯露天風呂6:00～//24:00止。(可穿拖鞋），旁邊休息室有免費罐裝飲料及罐裝啤酒。\n🔹 1樓和2樓之間，健身房 7:00～21:00\n🔹 東棟 4F 有烘焙 cafe 。（麵包跟蛋糕好好粗喔❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️） \n🔹小涵房號135，內線直撥房號即可，", "max_group_size": null, "booking_contact": null, "commission_rate": null, "google_maps_url": null, "airport_transfer": false, "concierge_service": true, "restaurants_count": null, "avg_price_per_night": null, "min_rooms_for_group": null, "group_rate_available": false, "has_michelin_restaurant": false}, {"id": "b6606126-2237-4eff-99e4-c410fcda1143", "fax": null, "name": "第一瀧本館", "brand": null, "notes": null, "phone": "0143-84-3311", "awards": null, "images": null, "address": "北海道登別市登別温泉町55番地", "city_id": "tokyo", "website": null, "category": "飯店 / Hotel", "currency": "USD", "latitude": null, "amenities": null, "is_active": true, "longitude": null, "region_id": null, "address_en": null, "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2026-03-16T07:42:46.764834+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "facilities": null, "highlights": null, "name_local": "第一滝本館", "room_types": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": null, "hotel_class": "standard", "is_featured": false, "price_range": null, "star_rating": 3, "best_seasons": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Dai-ichi Takimotokan", "workspace_id": "aed1bc23-7bbf-4c59-a8e3-12dbb3271f0a", "booking_email": null, "booking_phone": "0143-84-3311", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "butler_service": false, "certifications": null, "deleted_reason": null, "description_en": null, "dining_options": null, "group_friendly": true, "internal_notes": "🍽 用餐說明\n晚餐（依房型安排）：\n\n本館 3F：西式自助餐（Buffet）\n\n本館 5F／佳水館特定樓層：日式會席料理（需確認時間與地點）\n\n早餐：\n\n本館 3F：Buffet 早餐\n\n本館 5F：日式定食早餐\n\n🛁 大浴場使用資訊\n地點：西館 3F～2F\n\n開放時間（男女輪流更替）：\n\n大浴場（內湯）：24 小時\n\n露天風呂：05:00～24:00\n\n三溫暖：15:00～22:00\n\n休息區／飲品區：09:00～20:45\n\n注意事項：進入大浴場前，請先在更衣區準備好浴巾與毛巾\n\n🕒 飯店服務時間與資訊\n退房時間：10:00 前\n\n櫃台內線：撥打「0」\n\n棉被鋪設服務：17:45～21:00 之間提供\n\n製冰機位置：湯之里（本館5F／佳水館）\n\nWi-Fi：館內免費使用\n\nSSID：Takimoto（無需密碼）\n\n🧴 館內設施與服務（部分節錄）\n設施名稱\t營業時間\t說明\n湯之街（商店街）\t08:00～11:00、14:00～22:00（週六至22:00）\t飯店內部購物、美食與紀念品\n咖啡廳「はまなす」\t08:00～12:00、14:00～17:00\t提供咖啡與甜點，自由 Wi-Fi 空間\nそば屋「いでゆそば」\t11:30～14:00、18:00～24:00（週四休）\t知名蕎麥麵店，供應天婦羅、丼飯等\n芳療館 le Celebisu\t15:30～23:00（需預約）\t提供按摩與芳療服務（內線1142）\nGAME PLAZA\t08:00～21:45\t娛樂遊戲空間\n溫水泳池\t09:00～22:00（漂漂河 09:00～20:45）\t25米滑水道兒童友善設施\n露天風呂飲品吧\t15:30～20:20\t享受溫泉同時可品飲（在大浴場內）\n\n🗺 飯店樓層與設施導覽（右側地圖）\nLB～B1 樓層為主要公共設施所在\n\n重要設施集中於：\n\n本館：大浴場、餐廳、商店、遊戲區\n\n東館：櫃台（Front）\n\n南館：團體區／KTV／多功能室\n\n西館：大浴場、泳池、芳療館\n\n📌 其他注意事項\n飯店提供浴衣與拖鞋，全館可穿著行動\n\n房內無每日更換棉被，會於傍晚鋪設\n\n禁止於館內吸菸，請至指定吸菸區\n\n若選擇日式會席餐，需配合預訂時間用餐\n\n商店、按摩、泳池、餐廳皆可另收費", "max_group_size": null, "booking_contact": null, "commission_rate": null, "google_maps_url": null, "airport_transfer": false, "concierge_service": true, "restaurants_count": null, "avg_price_per_night": null, "min_rooms_for_group": null, "group_rate_available": false, "has_michelin_restaurant": false}, {"id": "b67ded9d-213c-4af2-809e-b976e044c874", "fax": null, "name": "名古屋東横INN中部機場2號館", "brand": null, "notes": null, "phone": "0569-38-1045", "awards": null, "images": null, "address": "愛知県常滑市セントレア4丁目3-1", "city_id": "tokyo", "website": null, "category": "飯店 / Hotel", "currency": "USD", "latitude": null, "amenities": null, "is_active": true, "longitude": null, "region_id": null, "address_en": null, "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2026-03-16T07:42:39.744988+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "facilities": null, "highlights": null, "name_local": "東横INN中部国際空港2", "room_types": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": null, "hotel_class": "standard", "is_featured": false, "price_range": null, "star_rating": 3, "best_seasons": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Toyoko Inn Chubu-Kokusai-Kuko 2", "workspace_id": "aed1bc23-7bbf-4c59-a8e3-12dbb3271f0a", "booking_email": null, "booking_phone": "0569-38-1045", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "butler_service": false,