c2-720b-4b42-82a5-698f9b781e55", "fax": null, "name": "Kobe Minato Onsen Ren", "brand": null, "notes": null, "phone": "078-381-7000", "awards": null, "images": null, "address": "日本〒650-0041 兵庫県神戸市中央区新港町1−1", "city_id": "kobe", "website": null, "category": "飯店 / Hotel", "currency": "USD", "latitude": null, "amenities": null, "is_active": true, "longitude": null, "region_id": null, "address_en": null, "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2026-03-16T07:42:49.089976+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "facilities": null, "highlights": null, "name_local": "神戸みなと温泉 蓮", "room_types": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": null, "hotel_class": "standard", "is_featured": false, "price_range": null, "star_rating": 3, "best_seasons": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Kobe Minato Onsen Ren", "workspace_id": "aed1bc23-7bbf-4c59-a8e3-12dbb3271f0a", "booking_email": null, "booking_phone": "078-381-7000", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "butler_service": false, "certifications": null, "deleted_reason": null, "description_en": null, "dining_options": null, "group_friendly": true, "internal_notes": "wifi密碼帳號在飯店指引上有註明 \n房號可以直接互撥 \n溫泉：06:00～24:00 \n住宿棟10樓（住宿旅客專用） \n及溫泉館1樓 \n（毛巾及浴巾現場皆有準備） \n晚餐：（餐廳住宿棟3樓万蓮） \n請隨身帶著手環 \n \n10樓另有酒吧可以一邊眺望夜景一邊喝酒🍺，營業時間為20:00～24:00 \n1樓賣店：8:00～22:00 \n \n泳池，瑜伽課，健身房…等均為另外預約付費。可與櫃檯接洽。 \n \n特別提醒： \n全室禁煙，如需吸菸請至吸煙區 \n睡衣僅限在房內使用 \n冰箱內飲料為自動計價 \n瓶裝水無料 \n館內消費全都會紀錄在房間的手環內、隔天退房時結算、請隨身帶著手環（含早晚餐報到）", "max_group_size": null, "booking_contact": null, "commission_rate": null, "google_maps_url": null, "airport_transfer": false, "concierge_service": true, "restaurants_count": null, "avg_price_per_night": null, "min_rooms_for_group": null, "group_rate_available": false, "has_michelin_restaurant": false}, {"id": "c15c3f4b-0389-4095-92fa-0495ceb1fe09", "fax": null, "name": "皆生溫泉東光園飯店", "brand": null, "notes": null, "phone": "0859-33-0121", "awards": null, "images": null, "address": "鳥取縣米子市皆生溫泉4-19-1", "city_id": "tokyo", "website": null, "category": "飯店 / Hotel", "currency": "USD", "latitude": null, "amenities": null, "is_active": true, "longitude": null, "region_id": null, "address_en": null, "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2026-03-16T07:42:51.635883+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "facilities": null, "highlights": null, "name_local": "皆生温泉 東光園", "room_types": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": null, "hotel_class": "standard", "is_featured": false, "price_range": null, "star_rating": 3, "best_seasons": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Kaike Onsen Tokoen Hotel", "workspace_id": "aed1bc23-7bbf-4c59-a8e3-12dbb3271f0a", "booking_email": null, "booking_phone": "0859-33-0121", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "butler_service": false, "certifications": null, "deleted_reason": null, "description_en": null, "dining_options": null, "group_friendly": true, "internal_notes": "皆生溫泉東光園溫泉飯店注意事項\n\n房間互撥  1+房號（阿琇 327 ）\n\n早餐   自助餐 4樓   \n7：00~憑鑰匙入場\n                   \n大浴場 地下1樓\n~24：00為止（最晚入場23：00）\n隔天早上5：00~\n男湯、女湯場地明早會互換\n\n大小毛巾在房內，請攜帶至大浴場使用，使用完畢請帶回房間\n\n浴衣和拖鞋館內、餐廳皆可來回使用\n\n浴衣穿法右下左上，切勿相反喲！\n\n抽煙請到1樓 ，賣店正前方庭院出口出來右邊戶外吸煙區，切勿在房內抽煙，會被罰錢喲！\n\n自動販賣機在1樓、3樓\n\n飯店WIFI ID：free_toukouen\n密碼：0859341111\n\n明日8：00出發，1樓集合\n7：50開始陸續上行李喲！\n\n已請飯店明早在1樓櫃檯附近設置行李置放區（百威旅遊  8：00出發  阿琇），可寄放行李後，再去用早餐喲！\n\n早call是6點，建議各位貴賓自己手機也要設個鬧鐘，以防飯店電話聲音太小叫不醒您喲！", "max_group_size": null, "booking_contact": null, "commission_rate": null, "google_maps_url": null, "airport_transfer": false, "concierge_service": true, "restaurants_count": null, "avg_price_per_night": null, "min_rooms_for_group": null, "group_rate_available": false, "has_michelin_restaurant": false}, {"id": "c1670f81-3181-4ba6-a891-3f04c00b9019", "fax": null, "name": "Dormy Inn 甲府丸の内", "brand": null, "notes": null, "phone": "055-225-5489", "awards": null, "images": null, "address": "山梨県甲府市丸の内1-1-12", "city_id": "tokyo", "website": null, "category": "飯店 / Hotel", "currency": "USD", "latitude": null, "amenities": null, "is_active": true, "longitude": null, "region_id": null, "address_en": null, "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2026-03-16T07:42:44.701893+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "facilities": null, "highlights": null, "name_local": "ドーミーイン甲府丸の内", "room_types": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": null, "hotel_class": "standard", "is_featured": false, "price_range": null, "star_rating": 3, "best_seasons": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Dormy Inn Kofu Marunouchi", "workspace_id": "aed1bc23-7bbf-4c59-a8e3-12dbb3271f0a", "booking_email": null, "booking_phone": "055-225-5489", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "butler_service": false, "certifications": null, "deleted_reason": null, "description_en": null, "dining_options": null, "group_friendly": true, "internal_notes": "👽領隊房號：\n☎️房號互撥：1+房號\n\n⏰明天叫早時間：\n🚌出發時間：\n🏨飯店大廳：1F\n\n🍞早餐餐廳：\n1樓（自助餐），06:30～09:30（最終入店 09:00）\n🌟自行用餐。🌟 無需餐券報房號即可。\n\n🇯🇵明天降雨：%\n🌡️溫度：度\n\n🔑房卡為感應式卡片。請妥善保管，遺失會索賠。房間會自動上鎖，房卡請隨身攜帶。\n💡入房插卡才有電。\n🌟退房時需歸還1樓櫃台或交給領隊協助退房\n\n📳WIFI密碼\nID：DORMYINN\nPASSWORD：dormyinn1234\n（會有房間說明書給大家）\n\n🚭全館禁煙🚬 \n吸菸室：1樓、6樓。\n🌟請勿心存僥倖，即使在外面抽，煙灰、煙蒂也請別帶回房間垃圾桶。開放至今，已發生多起，別團團員賠錢事件。\n\n☕️1樓有提供宵夜一碗拉麵，21:30-23:00。\n☕️1樓無料咖啡15:00-23:00。\n🍮冰箱布丁、礦泉水無料。\n\n♨️大浴場：9樓，勝運の湯。有無料冰棒。\n女性大浴場だけの特権は…「富士山」も見えます！\n入浴時間：15:00~10:00。三溫暖01:00-05:00關閉，其他時間可用。\n🚫謝絕刺青者入浴\n🌟請從房間攜帶大小毛巾，使用完帶回房間，必須重複使用。\n🥋可穿飯店提供的館內衣服和拖鞋至浴場。\n🙏入浴的禮節：\n致親愛的旅客\n使用溫泉時請遵守以下注意事項\n1. 請輕聱細語勿大聲喧嘩及嬉鬧\n2. 請勿把毛巾及頭髮浸泡在溫泉裡\n3. 衣服及拖鞋無法穿著進入浴場\n🌟入浴15分鐘，休息10分鐘。盡可能結伴同行，吃完飯後40分鐘後再泡，起身的一刻請讓心臟超過水面30秒以上再緩緩起身，避免危險。\n\n🏪便利商店：飯店出門左轉斜對面，3分鐘，LAWSON，24H。\n\n🏪超市：Lopia ロピア 甲府ヨドバシ店，出門左轉，營業至20:00。出門左轉，11分鐘。\n\n😱溫馨提醒\n🌟離開房間，請回頭看一眼書桌、衣櫥、冰箱、浴室。\n掉東西第一名：充電器。第二名：化妝包。第三名：耳環首飾類。\n\n🌟請將明日整天有可能使用的保溫瓶、個人藥品、小外套、行動電源、wifi機放在隨身行李，避免旅途中翻箱倒櫃。\n\n🌟明早一樓大廳，會有出發前行李置物的看板，建議您可以在吃早餐前，就先整理好行李置放，比較不會掉東西。", "max_group_size": null