 null, "group_friendly": true, "internal_notes": "含對面箱根Yunessan\n櫃檯checkin拿票\n\n園區地圖\nhttps://www.yunessun.com/yunessun/\nYunessan溫泉設施\n\n✨️帶泳衣即可，不需泳帽。\n（也可付費租借1200左右）\n不要穿館內作務衣，晚上會冷。\n\n入場掃描QRCode,會提供一次大小毛巾。\n置物櫃更衣室有。\n平日10：00-18：00\n假日10：00-19：00\n\n在4樓Lobby出發。\n\n🥣早餐 ：1F同晚餐廳 07:00-09:30、報房號即可。\n\n🌐飯店Wifi：   hotelkowakien\nWIFI密碼：0460824111\n\n♨️溫泉♨️：6F大浴場\n毛巾要從房間帶去浴場\n 開放時間：05:00-24:00\n\n🏡飯店門口全家便利店\n營業時間：07:00-23:00", "max_group_size": null, "booking_contact": null, "commission_rate": null, "google_maps_url": null, "airport_transfer": false, "concierge_service": true, "restaurants_count": null, "avg_price_per_night": null, "min_rooms_for_group": null, "group_rate_available": false, "has_michelin_restaurant": false}, {"id": "c7c43e91-431e-4401-b3c0-0b87844455c8", "fax": null, "name": "茅場町villa Fontaine", "brand": null, "notes": null, "phone": "03-5645-3355", "awards": null, "images": null, "address": "東京都中央区新川1-23-1", "city_id": "tokyo", "website": null, "category": "飯店 / Hotel", "currency": "USD", "latitude": null, "amenities": null, "is_active": true, "longitude": null, "region_id": null, "address_en": null, "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2026-03-16T07:42:36.465307+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "facilities": null, "highlights": null, "name_local": "ヴィラフォンテーヌ茅場町", "room_types": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": null, "hotel_class": "standard", "is_featured": false, "price_range": null, "star_rating": 3, "best_seasons": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Villa Fontaine Kayabacho", "workspace_id": "aed1bc23-7bbf-4c59-a8e3-12dbb3271f0a", "booking_email": null, "booking_phone": "03-5645-3355", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "butler_service": false, "certifications": null, "deleted_reason": null, "description_en": null, "dining_options": null, "group_friendly": true, "internal_notes": "📝 注意事項:\n茅場町villa Fontaine\n\n⭕️連住兩天不換房，貴重物品請鎖在行李箱裡面，不喜歡清掃人員進入房間打掃，請將請勿打擾的牌子掛出來。\n⭕️請在本館集合、用早餐、後天早上放行李。\n⭕️房間皆在別館，進入必須用房卡開啟。\n\n👽領隊房號：\n☎️房號互撥：2+房間號碼\n\n⏰明天叫早時間：\n🚌出發時間：\n\n🏨飯店本館大廳1F集合\n\n🍞早餐餐廳：本館與別館1樓（自助餐）06:30-09:30\n⭐️自行用餐⭐️有餐卷\n\n🪥牙刷，睡衣、茶包、咖啡等備品，如有需要，請在1樓拿取，房間裡面只有毛巾、沐浴用品。\n\n🌞明天降雨：%\n🌡️溫度：度\n\n🔑感應式房卡。\n💡入房要插卡才有電。\n鑰匙請交還給本館一樓櫃檯，或給阿霖協助退房。\n\n📳WIFI密碼\nID: villafontaine-ky\nPASSWORD：VFKY2220\n\n🚭全館禁煙🚬 吸菸區：本館1樓大廳內\n⭐️請勿心存僥倖，即使在外面抽，煙灰、煙蒂也請別帶回房間垃圾桶。開放至今，已發生多起，別團團員賠錢事件。\n\n🏪超商：\n新館斜對面7-11，走路20秒。24H。\n本館斜對面，過馬路走路1分鐘，全家，24H。\n🏪超市：\nHanamasa ：飯店本館對面走路4分鐘，營業6:00-25:00。\nAEON：飯店大門左轉5-6分鐘。營業至23:00。\n🏪藥妝：スギ藥局，本館對面，營業時間08:00-21:00。\n\n😱溫馨提醒：回國當晚注意事項\n\n⭕️雖然很累，還是請各位盡可能在睡覺前整理好行李，避免掉東西。\n\n🇹🇼桃園降雨：10%\n🇹🇼桃園氣溫：12-18度\n\n⭐️整理行李的時候，請將瓶裝標示容量100cc以上的液體（乳霜、護手霜、人工淚液、泡麵、面膜、飲料etc）、尖銳物品（水果刀、刮鬍刀、指甲剪、食物剪、修眉刀、瑞士刀etc）放入行李箱中。\n\n⭐️打火機、行動電源可以隨身攜帶，不可托運。防風式打火機必須丟棄。\n\n⭐️請再想想床上、衣櫥、浴室、冰箱、保險箱、充電器etc，有無遺失任何物品。\n\n⭐️明早飯店本館1樓大廳櫃檯左側會有行李置物看板。建議您吃早餐前，先整理好行李置放，比較不會掉東西。", "max_group_size": null, "booking_contact": null, "commission_rate": null, "google_maps_url": null, "airport_transfer": false, "concierge_service": true, "restaurants_count": null, "avg_price_per_night": null, "min_rooms_for_group": null, "group_rate_available": false, "has_michelin_restaurant": false}, {"id": "c806b988-d7e9-489d-81dd-6a9c5facb906", "fax": null, "name": "清邁四季度假村", "brand": "Four Seasons", "notes": null, "phone": null, "awards": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "chiang-mai", "website": null, "category": "resort", "currency": "USD", "latitude": null, "amenities": null, "is_active": true, "longitude": null, "region_id": null, "address_en": null, "country_id": "thailand", "created_at": "2025-12-17T15:12:39.090728+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "facilities": {"bar": true, "gym": true, "spa": true, "pool": true, "concierge": true, "restaurant": true}, "highlights": ["梯田稻田景觀", "蘭納建築風格", "水牛耕田體驗", "得獎水療中心"], "name_local": null, "room_types": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "位於Mae R