WORD：liber1113\n\n🚭全館禁煙🚬 吸菸室：1、3樓。1樓在進飯店大門最右邊，3樓在中間餐廳後面，都是室內吸煙室。房間內吸煙真的會罰錢，請不要心存僥倖。\n\n🏨飯店內禮品店：1F 08:00-21:00沒有退稅。\n\n♨大浴場3F(11:00~01: 00，06:00-09:00)\n ⭐️需要感應式房卡\n ⭐️大小毛巾浴場有，不能帶回房間。可以穿飯店的睡衣去泡湯，泡15分鐘休10分鐘，⭕️起身前一\n定要讓心臟超過水面30秒再緩緩起身。盡可能結伴同行。若有大片刺青會被拒絕入浴，敬請見諒。\n ⭐️可以穿拖鞋至3樓泡湯，但不可以穿到大廳與餐廳。\n ⭐️3F有有料按摩椅¥300一次。\n ⭐️房間浴室有超貼心無料涼感貼布，但….不好用。\n ⭐️房間有烘鞋機。3樓有洗衣機，一次¥400。\n\n🏪便利商店：出飯店大廳門右轉2分鐘7-11，24H。\n⭐️現在塑膠袋要收費。\n\n😱溫馨提醒\n⭐️3樓中間餐廳後面有平台，走出去可以看到天保山的摩天輪漂亮的夜景。不能我自己知道。\n\n⭐️日夜溫差大，出門請攜帶禦寒衣物、雨具、行動電源、wifi機、空曠風大吹了頭會痛藥。", "max_group_size": null, "booking_contact": null, "commission_rate": null, "google_maps_url": null, "airport_transfer": false, "concierge_service": true, "restaurants_count": null, "avg_price_per_night": null, "min_rooms_for_group": null, "group_rate_available": false, "has_michelin_restaurant": false}, {"id": "dd494571-20e4-47e6-9fba-93c9e97670ee", "fax": null, "name": "首爾新羅酒店", "brand": "Shilla", "notes": null, "phone": null, "awards": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "seoul", "website": null, "category": "city", "currency": "USD", "latitude": null, "amenities": null, "is_active": true, "longitude": null, "region_id": null, "address_en": null, "country_id": "korea", "created_at": "2025-12-17T15:12:39.090728+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "facilities": {"bar": true, "gym": true, "spa": true, "pool": true, "concierge": true, "restaurant": true}, "highlights": ["韓式奢華代表", "景福宮步行可達", "頂級水療中心", "免稅店"], "name_local": null, "room_types": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "韓式奢華代表，位於景福宮與明洞附近。融合傳統韓式美學與現代設計。", "hotel_class": "luxury", "is_featured": true, "price_range": "4", "star_rating": 5, "best_seasons": null, "country_code": "KR", "english_name": "The Shilla Seoul", "workspace_id": "aed1bc23-7bbf-4c59-a8e3-12dbb3271f0a", "booking_email": null, "booking_phone": null, "data_verified": false, "display_order": 61, "butler_service": false, "certifications": null, "deleted_r