梯的時候要用房卡感應電梯\n🏨 房間有館內服，全館內可以穿館內服跟室內拖鞋移動，如果尺寸不合，可以到4樓溫泉櫃台更換。\n🪒刮鬍刀、浴帽，可以在本館電梯前拿取。\n\n♨ 溫泉4樓：（需先到本館3樓大廳，搭乘另一電梯或走樓梯到溫泉區4樓）5:00-9:00 ，11:00-02:00。\n3樓本館大廳旁有寄放鞋子的櫃子，赤腳前往4樓溫泉，spa櫃檯。\n🚫九歲以上不得混浴，謝絕刺青者及未滿3歲及尚在包尿包的小孩入浴\n⭐️不需要攜帶大、小毛巾，只需攜帶房卡。\n⭐️泡溫泉15分鐘休息10分鐘。盡可能結伴同行，吃完飯後40分鐘後再泡。\n⭐️館內餐廳消費直接記房帳，退房時於3樓櫃檯還鑰匙時一併結帳。\n\n👩‍🍳付費餐廳：本館6樓，營業至21:30。\n\n📳WIFI密碼\nID：EURASIA \nPASSWORD：12345678\n\n🚭全館禁煙🚬 \n吸菸區：1樓公車站旁、3樓聯絡通道、本館4樓溫泉區附近\n⭐️請勿心存僥倖，即使在外面抽，煙灰、煙蒂也請別帶回房間垃圾桶。開放至今，已發生多起，別團團員賠錢事件。\n\n🛒売店：本館3樓，5:00-02:00\n櫃檯沒人時，請至check in櫃檯結帳\n\n🎆本館10樓有露天展望，看得到迪士尼煙火（只有本館右邊的電梯才會到10樓）\n\n🚫房間及浴室內禁止染頭髮\n\n⭐️三樓會有出發前行李置物處的看板，建議您可以在吃早餐前，就先整理好行李置放，比較不會掉東西。\n\n❗️從飯店出發要注意不要坐到30分出發往浦安的車", "max_group_size": null, "booking_contact": null, "commission_rate": null, "google_maps_url": null, "airport_transfer": false, "concierge_service": true, "restaurants_count": null, "avg_price_per_night": null, "min_rooms_for_group": null, "group_rate_available": false, "has_michelin_restaurant": false}, {"id": "deb4ed41-b98f-4c1d-93ac-28ae5c8c645c", "fax": null, "name": "Ark熊本城前", "brand": null, "notes": null, "phone": null, "awards": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "kumamoto", "website": null, "category": "飯店 / Hotel", "currency": "USD", "latitude": null, "amenities": null, "is_active": true, "longitude": null, "region_id": null, "address_en": null, "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2026-03-16T07:42:44.701893+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "facilities": null, "highlights": null, "name_local": "アークホテル熊本城前", "room_types": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": null, "hotel_class": "standard", "is_featured": false, "price_range": null, "star_rating": 3, "best_seasons": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Ark Hotel Kumamoto-Jo Mae", "workspace_id": "aed1bc23-7bbf-4c59-a8e3-12dbb3271f0a", "booking_email": null, "booking_phone": null, "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "butler_service": false, "certifications": null, "deleted_reason": null, "description_en": null, "dining_options": null, "group_friendly": true, "internal_notes": "🕕 起床與早餐\n\t•\t🔔 請於 06:15 自行設鬧鐘，飯店不提供晨喚服務。\n\t•\t🍽️ 早餐地點：10 樓，06:30 開始供應，需攜帶餐券。\n\t•\t🧳 建議用早餐時先拿大件行李放至大廳寄存區，可避免退房時人多等電梯。\n\n🧳 退房與行李處理\n\t•\t📦 07:50 請將行李放置於指定處並交回房卡。\n\t•\t🕵️‍♂️ 離開前請確認房內是否遺留私人物品。\n\n\n🚶 出發與集合\n\t•\t🕗 08:00 準時出發，請於 07:50 前完成所有準備事項。\n\t•\t🧑‍💼 領隊房號：＿＿＿＿（請補填）\n\n🔧 其他資訊\n\t•\t🔌 Wifi 密碼：請查看房卡信封。\n\t•\t🚬 吸菸室位於大門右側。\n\t•\t🛏️ 本飯店無提供大床房，敬請見諒。", "max_group_size": null, "booking_contact": null, "commission_rate": null, "google_maps_url": null, "airport_transfer": false, "concierge_service": true, "restaurants_count": null, "avg_price_per_night": null, "min_rooms_for_group": null, "group_rate_available": false, "has_michelin_restaurant": false}, {"id": "deb75cc7-a3c7-404d-b58e-fcc7b7c0d2f3", "fax": null, "name": "安縵京都", "brand": "Aman", "notes": null, "phone": null, "awards": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "kyoto", "website": null, "category": "resort", "currency": "USD", "latitude": null, "amenities": null, "is_active": true, "longitude": null, "region_id": null, "address_en": null, "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2025-12-17T15:12:39.090728+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "facilities": {"bar": true, "gym": true, "spa": true, "pool": false, "butler": true, "concierge": true, "restaurant": true}, "highlights": ["米其林二星酒店", "32公頃私人森林", "極致私密體驗", "頂級懷石料理"], "name_local": null, "room_types": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "隱身於左大文字山腳下32公頃森林中的秘境酒店。26間客房融入自然環境，提供極致私密的京都體驗。米其林二星酒店。", "hotel_class": "ultra-luxury", "is_featured": true, "price_range": "5", "star_rating": 5, "best_seasons": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Aman Kyoto", "workspace_id": "aed1bc23-7bbf-4c59-a8e3-12dbb3271f0a", "booking_email": null, "booking_phone": null, "data_verified": false, "display_order": 10, "butler_service": false, "certifications": nu