式卡片，退房時需歸還\n⭐️房卡只有一張，有需要在櫃檯可以多做，遺失一張¥1000日幣。\n⭐️電梯有分高樓層、低樓層電梯，入門後的左側1-20樓，右側20樓以上，可在20樓轉乘。\n⭐️乾濕分離、浴缸深，有小朋友的貴賓請注意不要嗆到。放水是定時開關，不是有派米啊。\n\n📳WIFI密碼\nSSID：PRINCE-HOTEL\nPASSWORD：welcomeph\n\n🚭全館禁煙🚬， 吸菸：1樓大門右側室外吸煙區\n\n🏪便利商店：飯店1樓，營業至22:00。\n全家便利商店在超市斜對面，走路約7分鐘，24H。\n🏪超市：出大門右側街道直走就能看到Valor Otsu走路約5分鐘，營業至20:00。\n⭐️街道暗暗的要注意安全，別跌進水溝裡。\n\n😱溫馨提醒\n⭐️離開房間，請回頭看一眼書桌、衣櫥、冰箱、浴室。\n掉東西第一名：充電器。第二名：化妝包。第三名：耳環首飾類。\n\n⭐️明早1樓會有行李置物處（）的看板，建議您可以在吃早餐前，就先整理好行李置放，比較不會掉東西。\n\n⭐️盡可能想一下一整天會用到的東西（手機、行動電源、wifi機、藥品、保溫杯），先從行李箱中拿出來，到時放在明天巴士上，這樣才不用在旅途中翻箱倒櫃。", "max_group_size": null, "booking_contact": null, "commission_rate": null, "google_maps_url": null, "airport_transfer": false, "concierge_service": true, "restaurants_count": null, "avg_price_per_night": null, "min_rooms_for_group": null, "group_rate_available": false, "has_michelin_restaurant": false}, {"id": "e6efc9dd-3cac-4519-afc6-c7d3057763db", "fax": null, "name": "曼谷四季酒店", "brand": "Four Seasons", "notes": null, "phone": null, "awards": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "bangkok", "website": null, "category": "city", "currency": "USD", "latitude": null, "amenities": null, "is_active": true, "longitude": null, "region_id": null, "address_en": null, "country_id": "thailand", "created_at": "2025-12-17T15:12:39.090728+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "facilities": {"bar": true, "gym": true, "spa": true, "pool": true, "concierge": true, "restaurant": true}, "highlights": ["2025年最佳新酒店", "河畔歷史街區", "米其林餐廳", "水療與瑜伽"], "name_local": null, "room_types": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": "2020年開幕，位於昭披耶河畔歷史街區。299間客房融合泰式傳統與現代設計。2025年最佳新酒店。", "hotel_class": "luxury", "is_featured": true, "price_range": "4", "star_rating": 5, "best_seasons": null, "country_code": "TH", "english_name": "Four Seasons Hotel Bangkok at Chao Phraya River", "workspace_id": "aed1bc23-7bbf-4c59-a8e3-12dbb3271f0a", "booking_email": null, "booking_phone": null, "data_verified": fa