null, "dining_options": null, "group_friendly": true, "internal_notes": "👽領隊房號：\n☎️房號互撥：7+房間號碼\n\n⏰明天叫早時間：\n🚌出發時間：\n🇯🇵明天降雨：%\n🌡️溫度：度\n\n🍞早餐餐廳：\n1樓（自助餐）07：00自行用餐\n🌟自行用餐，有餐卷\n\n🏨飯店櫃檯：於2樓還鑰匙，或早上出發前在1樓給領隊即可。請在1樓集合。\n\n🌟感應式鑰匙，需退房。\n🌟需房卡才能驅動住宿的樓層，其他樓層無法去。\n🌟晚上00:00-06:00，一樓大門自動上鎖，進來必須要有房卡。\n🌟無礦泉水，電梯旁有飲水機，請從房間帶容器取用。2樓有無料軟飲，使用至22:00。\n\n\n📳WIFI密碼\nSSID : MiyakoCityOsakaHommachi \nPASSWORD：miyako385\n🌟如果各位第一個wifi連不上，可以打開電視按紅框這個，可以找到您房間專屬的密碼。\n\n🚭全館禁煙🚬 吸菸室：2樓。\n嚴禁在房間吸菸，請不要心存僥倖，抓到真的會罰錢。解封以來已發生多次吸菸被罰事件。\n\n🏪便利商店:出門左邊對街1分鐘，7-11，24H\n\n🏪超市:出門左邊直走2分鐘，KOHYO南船橋，24H\n\n😱溫馨提醒\n\n🌟明早飯店1樓有行李置物看板。建議您吃早餐前，先整理好行李置放，比較不會掉東西。", "max_group_size": null, "booking_contact": null, "commission_rate": null, "google_maps_url": null, "airport_transfer": false, "concierge_service": true, "restaurants_count": null, "avg_price_per_night": null, "min_rooms_for_group": null, "group_rate_available": false, "has_michelin_restaurant": false}, {"id": "f3200f6e-610f-4baf-95b8-12e26c02871d", "fax": null, "name": "修善寺溫泉酒店 滝亭", "brand": null, "notes": null, "phone": "0558-98-1111", "awards": null, "images": null, "address": "〒410-2416 静岡県伊豆市修善寺970-1", "city_id": "tokyo", "website": null, "category": "飯店 / Hotel", "currency": "USD", "latitude": null, "amenities": null, "is_active": true, "longitude": null, "region_id": null, "address_en": null, "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2026-03-16T07:42:44.111124+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "facilities": null, "highlights": null, "name_local": "修善寺温泉ホテル 滝亭", "room_types": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": null, "hotel_class": "standard", "is_featured": false, "price_range": null, "star_rating": 3, "best_seasons": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "Takitei Shuzenji Hotel", "workspace_id": "aed1bc23-7bbf-4c59-a8e3-12dbb3271f0a", "booking_email": null, "booking_phone": "0558-98-1111", "data_verified": false, "display_order": 0, "butler_service": false, "certifications": null, "deleted_reason": null, "description_en": null, "dining_options": null, "group_friendly": true, "internal_notes": "🛎 1F 設施與服務\n服務台／賣店營業時間：06:30～22:00\n\n夜間無人時，大廳正門將自動上鎖。若有需要可撥打：\n\n📞 24小時聯絡電話：070-1399-5399\n\n📞 緊急電話：090-2587-3086\n\n♨️ 2F 大浴場與露天溫泉\n早上：05:30～09:30\n\n下午／晚上：13:30～24:00\n\n✅ 請從房間攜帶以下備品前往溫泉：\n\n毛巾、溫泉浴巾、洗漱用品、牙刷、牙膏、化妝水等\n\n❌ 禁止將毛巾放入溫泉池中。\n\n✅ 為避免滑倒，請於浴後擦乾再行走。\n\n🏓 娛樂設施\n乒乓球間：09:00～21:00\n\n自動販賣機區：24小時開放（分布於2F、5～8F）\n\n🍽 3F／4F 餐廳「サムライ」\n早餐時間：07:00～09:00\n\n晚餐時間：18:00～20:00\n\n※如有特殊需求，請事先告知\n\n🛏 客房注意事項\n冰箱：請自行插電啟用（旋轉開關）\n\n空調：請使用開關切換冷／暖氣，調整適溫\n\n插座：請注意插頭方向以免無法啟用\n\n房內提供浴衣、浴衣帶、牙刷與刮鬍刀\n\n大浴場用的籃子放在房內衣櫃內\n\n📌 備註提醒\n貴重物品：請務必放入房內保險櫃中，否則遺失恕不負責\n\n緊急聯絡方式：24小時服務專線（如上）\n\n✍️ 手寫備註\n晚餐：17:30 開始\n\n早餐：7:00 開始", "max_group_size": null, "booking_contact": null, "commission_rate": null, "google_maps_url": null, "airport_transfer": false, "concierge_service": true, "restaurants_count": null, "avg_price_per_night": null, "min_rooms_for_group": null, "group_rate_available": false, "has_michelin_restaurant": false}, {"id": "f33a37b4-a0fc-4244-a41f-838175ff47b3", "fax": null, "name": "OMO5 小樽", "brand": "星野集團 - OMO", "notes": null, "phone": null, "awards": null, "images": null, "address": null, "city_id": "tokyo", "website": null, "category": "都市精選飯店", "currency": "USD", "latitude": null, "amenities": null, "is_active": true, "longitude": null, "region_id": null, "address_en": null, "country_id": "japan", "created_at": "2026-04-04T11:39:13.635+00:00", "created_by": null, "deleted_at": null, "deleted_by": null, "facilities": null, "highlights": null, "name_local": null, "room_types": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-15T21:18:09.793607+00:00", "updated_by": null, "description": null, "hotel_class": "精選商務", "is_featured": false, "price_range": null, "star_rating": 3, "best_seasons": null, "country_code": "JP", "english_name": "OMO5 Otaru", "workspace_id": "aed1bc23-7bbf-4c59-a8e3-12dbb3271f0a", "booking_email": null, "booking_phone": null, "data_verified": false, "display_or